<p>I tried a conference call to myself on the weekend and it worked fine! I couldn&#39;t get it to work with Mac Skype (couldn&#39;t figure out how send my phone number, how does one send a DTMF tones in Mac Skype?) but that&#39;s Skype&#39;s fault and I am sure will be easily remedied. This will be great for impromptu calls.</p>
